Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveSinger, Davido, has responded to a tweep, who claimed that his family, The Adelekes, will use the resources of the state to develop Atlanta in the United States.
Davido’s uncle, Ademola Adeleke, had won the Osun governorship election on Saturday and he was presented with the Certificate of Return on Wednesday.
Reacting to a photo of Adeleke holding firmly onto his Certificate of Return, a tweep, Atiyuski said, “Las las Adeleke will use Osun State money to build Atlanta Georgia. What a pity for the people of Osun State.”
Responding to him, Davido said, “We’ve had 4 mansions in Atlanta since 94. #FACTCHECK”
